'''联合国和平广场'''（United Nations Peace Plaza）位于美国[[独立城_(密苏里州)|独立城 (密苏里州)]]，开辟于1997年10月27日，2003年4月25日联合国秘书长[[Kofi_Annan|Kofi Annan]]为其正式揭幕<ref>[https://docs.google.com/viewer?a=v&q=cache:QUHXaMNbZ1gJ:una-kc.org/NL/Jul-Aug-04.pdf+statue+by+corbin+u.n.+peace+plaza&hl=en&gl=us&pid=bl&srcid=ADGEESihvrKqTZB6PKLeht1_82BCN5B_4vTGkWgWoPP7bzvKrb744-ynpKZaLTrJS9g9frD5YdqKLXrPvP35y8Ot5t9eNVLrLoGNRAsah_4cKWGK7gOl1mB3F1ODkL3gef8HwaMa8zwd&sig=AHIEtbR59DW_2ILlJSrvfEKFvHCQ8wjQZw "...Peace Plaza dedicatory ceremony in Independence April 25, 2003..."] Quickview of July, 2004 UNA-GCK newsletter report.</ref>，其创作者称之为“世界上唯一献给[[联合国|联合国]]维持和平部队战士的纪念碑 ...”<ref>[http://una-kc.org/Outreach/UN-Peace-Plaza.htm Partial explanation of the Plaza and Statue] {{Wayback|url=http://una-kc.org/Outreach/UN-Peace-Plaza.htm |date=20180809204405 }} at website of "United Nations Association - Greater Kansas City Chapter."(UNA-GKC)</ref>。12.5英尺的雕像被雕塑家汤姆·科尔宾命名为“女孩与鸽子”<ref>[http://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:jsIo4N8S9mMJ:www.evareynoldsfinearts.com/ersys/document_downloads/bio_tom_corbin.pdfs&cd=3&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=us "Artist and Biography of Tom Corbin"] lists the U.N. Peace Plaza as one of his works.</ref><ref>[http://www.amazon.com/Tom-Corbin-Inevitable-Beverly-Bellinger/dp/0977330702 "Tom Corbin: The Inevitable Artist" by Beverly Bellinger] Biography of the sculptor Tom Corbin published in 2006, previewed at Amazon.Com</ref>。

2006年12月11日，联合国秘书长安南在密苏里州独立城的杜鲁门总统图书馆作任内最后发言<ref>[http://www.trumanlibrary.org/audio/KofiAnnanSpeech.html Audio of Annan's "Farewell Address" December 11, 2006] at trumanlibrary.org</ref><ref>[http://www.un.org/News/ossg/sg/stories/statments_full.asp?statID=40 Text of December 11, 2006 speech] {{Wayback|url=http://www.un.org/News/ossg/sg/stories/statments_full.asp?statID=40 |date=20110712082554 }} at United Nations official website</ref>，然后来到联合国和平广场献花<ref>[http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_multi=EIMB|&p_product=EIMB&p_theme=gatehouse&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&s_dispstring=annan,%20hite%20AND%20date%281/14/2006%20to%208/14/2007%29&p_field_date-0=YMD_date&p_params_date-0=date:B,E&p_text_date-0=1/14/2006%20to%208/14/2007%29&p_field_advanced-0=&p_text_advanced-0=%28annan,%20hite%29&xcal_numdocs=20&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&xcal_useweights=no Annan pays tribute at U.N. Peace Plaza] Robert Hite, ''The Examiner'', 2006-12-12</ref>。

